{"tid":676239,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"爆相爆片：意國已出局　瑞銀照估捧世盃","createTime":"2018-05-24T08:11:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-24T08:23:37.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1566a70b3163abdc88602887bac92565febe1d04","tid":676239,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T08:11:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180524/20400024\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180524%2F20400024&d=l%2Bs1Dl%2BLTlmF99EQBzEaT6NGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=2177d089\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180524%2F20400024&h=e8066bf3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180524/20400024</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年05月24日 <br />\n<br />\n爆相爆片：意國已出局　瑞銀照估捧世盃<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180524/large/a1105a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180524%2Flarge%2Fa1105a.gif&h=ae2f558b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■投行瑞銀份世界盃報告，指意大利（紅框示）奪冠機會為1.6%。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n世界盃即將開鑼，博彩公司紛紛開出32隊參賽隊伍奪標賠率，巴西、德國、西班牙、阿根廷同法國多數被視為5大熱門，投資銀行瑞銀早前聘請18位分析師，好似預測股市走勢咁，用精密電腦經過專業分析，撰寫詳細世界盃報告，當中得出「神級」結果，意大利今屆奪冠機會為1.6%，同主辦國俄羅斯一樣，但重點係：意大利根本喺外圍賽已出局，有乜可能奪冠？<br />\n<br />\n撰寫報告嘅主管喺前言話，希望呢份報告有助大家作出相關嘅投資決定，係咪令人好驚奇？但報告中都有一段提到，好多球隊未能打入決賽周，當中最令人可惜嘅係意大利，因為意大利係4屆冠軍云云，又話要向意大利致敬，但呢段文字解釋被質疑可能係後期加入「補鑊」，唔少網民諷刺話「點解無北韓？」、「佢寫下次啊！」  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n爆相爆片：P牌七人車　烈日下自焚<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n今日焦點‧即聽"},{"pid":"bb938adcff0d03c85a54342e751bc1a5eac5faf8","tid":676239,"uid":38049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T08:16:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e3cc33a1e9c31fea810802169d8934fb6da5104","tid":676239,"uid":36970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T08:20:07.000Z","msg":"England 8.5 已經唔洗再睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bbe122bd1d1504387b4e43ad55d43544e642223","tid":676239,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T08:23:37.000Z","msg":"法國低過英撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}